Casper;;49;;51;;PG;;Casper (voiced by Malachi Pearson) is a kind young ghost who peacefully haunts a mansion in Maine. When specialist James Harvey (Bill Pullman) arrives to communicate with Casper and his fellow spirits, he brings along his teenage daughter, Kat (Christina Ricci). Casper quickly falls in love with Kat, but their budding relationship is complicated not only by his transparent state, but also by his troublemaking apparition uncles and their mischievous antics.;;Fantasy,Kids & family;;Brad Silberling;;1995;;Christina Ricci,Bill Pullman,Cathy Moriarty,Eric Idle,Malachi Pearson,Joe Nipote,Joe Alaskey,Brad Garrett;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/casper